{"tid":437750,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"卡卡奧蘭多城最終章淚灑當場，三年美好回憶難集中作賽","createTime":"2017-10-16T09:27:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T10:50:35.000Z","uid":60286,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"128c56b625066fff02ef289ef0f0bb035fc26fa5","tid":437750,"uid":60286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:27:02.000Z","msg":"35歲的卡卡今天最後一次披上奧蘭多城戰衣，未開賽已雙眼通紅。無奈球隊主場以0︰1不敵哥倫布機員，未能完美告別。他賽後感謝球迷及球會，指奧蘭多城永在心中。他在更衣室內逐一與隊友、管理層及班主擁抱，準備迎接新挑戰。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/16/172348_817458bff4ac01c55c8f5a4669b61e41.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F16%2F172348_817458bff4ac01c55c8f5a4669b61e41.jpg&h=be5a1873&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>卡卡踢足全場 罰球楣頂高出</strong><br />\n35歲的卡卡（Kak&aacute;）2014年轉投奧蘭多城（Orlando City）至今，球隊未曾打入季後賽。<span style=\"color: red;\">他早前宣布婉拒奧蘭多城續約，戰罷今仗對哥倫布機員便會離隊，下周對費城聯不會上陣。他開賽前在奏美國國歌時已雙眼通紅，眼角流淚。</span>卡卡戴上隊長臂章踢足全場，曾主射罰球僅僅高出。最終球隊被卡馬拉在66分鐘射入全場唯一入球，以0︰1不敵哥倫布機員。奧蘭多城33戰38分列東岸尾二。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/16/172430_ea5dc286b5c52f6dcef0280863c586ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F16%2F172430_ea5dc286b5c52f6dcef0280863c586ae.jpg&h=66af966d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩個小球迷衝入草地，只為了與卡卡擁抱。（美聯社）<br />\n今季貢獻6球及5個助攻的卡卡最後一次代表奧蘭多城，賽後顯露出感性一面︰「今天很特別，我腦海中不斷想起過去3年在奧蘭多城的美好回憶，今天只想說謝謝。感謝球會、球迷、隊友，我會想念你們，奧蘭多城代表的獅子永在我心。」<span style=\"color: red;\">卡卡認為今場極難踢，因為場上很多湧上心頭，難以集中比賽。賽後他在更衣室內逐一與隊友、管理層、班主擁抱，又為球迷簽名，就此告別美職。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/16/172504_537b5efbee4e7e6f147da1f57b9746fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F16%2F172504_537b5efbee4e7e6f147da1f57b9746fd.jpg&h=66a0bd8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/16/172510_89046430a9bfe614f771ed88307bc59b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F16%2F172510_89046430a9bfe614f771ed88307bc59b.jpg&h=71d86256&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">卡卡未有掛靴的念頭</span>，目前盛傳回到巴西效力母會聖保羅。該會會長巴路斯透露有可能成事︰「一切仍未確實，一定都有可能。若他想回來，我們會盡一切努力助他達成心願。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/16/172534_5dbdf1ec50849f4f1885a509d7e07340.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F16%2F172534_5dbdf1ec50849f4f1885a509d7e07340.jpg&h=5c682f68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IvW-ESByDqs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIvW-ESByDqs&d=Ui2P69gUQGZudWyCemU58G6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=ed05f5ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IvW-ESByDqs</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6vht5QM1DSY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6vht5QM1DSY&d=Ui2P69gUQGZudWyCemU58G6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=3790b912\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6vht5QM1DSY</a><br />\n卡卡美職告別戰精華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/16/172651_748e6e40cd65c50cde405bafed7bb259.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F16%2F172651_748e6e40cd65c50cde405bafed7bb259.jpg&h=dd93d819&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Gvv5Ftcn1XU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGvv5Ftcn1XU&d=Ui2P69gUQGZudWyCemU58G6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=974626a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Gvv5Ftcn1XU</a><br />\n<br />\n來源：hk01"},{"pid":"ac3929c78cc6004e662ba2640aef15584e044d04","tid":437750,"uid":60286,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:36:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望仲可以係歐洲賽場見到佢"},{"pid":"db5b26da0540363f821c6e1b568d0be163423f16","tid":437750,"uid":51022,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:38:17.000Z","msg":"細個就係睇佢係ac比賽而愛上足球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2087cf7d90abefaa84502eb506b48b46bd2d9df0","tid":437750,"uid":4957,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T10:01:21.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 買撚左你主勝"},{"pid":"097f20460b649b7a016c26a9ef9cfd0a005ce200","tid":437750,"uid":5303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T10:05:09.000Z","msg":"得6入球5助攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返巴西踢夠唔夠班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4269f33101773447089229c2148478797f9a41cc","tid":437750,"uid":84286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T10:26:28.000Z","msg":"美職得啖笑，啲假波多撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c205c1b82e05ac42802abbf4c5e2a66ac0ad026","tid":437750,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T10:30:52.000Z","msg":"原來仲未退休<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"003b0bd505352905275e2af945a8eeb695f93408","tid":437750,"uid":137694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T10:38:23.000Z","msg":"第一年開始睇波就係卡卡最高峰嗰時，估唔到而家已經就退役<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02cb8e1d80e1cde3e71ba8056bba4852c2fca2a9","tid":437750,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T10:41:53.000Z","msg":"美職 主場好少豬 重要告別戰 又打假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc876d89698ac1ece631e92a3abbdac5a84e2fd6","tid":437750,"uid":91195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T10:49:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母 買撚左你主勝</blockquote><br />\n佢買咗客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9029bde3f726b7ab0d7dc961881f66a6f33b768d","tid":437750,"uid":9924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T10:50:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望仲可以係歐洲賽場見到佢</blockquote><br />\n幾多歲呀仲踢<br />\n你估佢仲係十幾年前個隻跑狗咩"}]}